<plot>This Universal "Name Band Musical" short headlines Tommy Tucker and His Orchestra and features Don Brown and his group singing most of the songs, while Corrine and Tito Valdez dance to one number. Music includes "Sleepy-Time Gal",Chopin's "Nocturne No. 2", "Spell of the Moon" and "Boarding House Jump." Universal production number was 1302, which Universal used again on a 1954 musical short called "Road Show."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?246881</url></doc>
